'''Ahmed Fawzi Saleh''' (yavutse 1 Mutarama 1981), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri Egiputa . <ref>http://www.filmstarts.de/personen/523761.html</ref> Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa film izwi cyane ''Poisonous Roses'' . <ref>https://dailynewsegypt.com/2018/05/28/finding-humanity-in-egyptian-tanners-district-in-ahmed-fawzi-salehs-poisonous-roses/</ref> Usibye gukora firime, Saleh numuntu uharanira imibereho myiza. <ref name="egypttoday">https://www.egypttoday.com/Article/4/40881/World-premiere-of-Poisonous-Roses-to-take-place-at-IFFR</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 1 Mutarama 1981 i Alegizandiriya, mu Misiri . Yabonye impamyabumenyi mu mateka yakuye muri kaminuza ya Suez Canal hanyuma abona impamyabumenyi yo gufata amashusho mu Ishuri Rikuru rya Sinema rya Cairo mu 2009. <ref name="IFFR">https://iffr.com/en/persons/ahmed-fawzi-saleh</ref> <ref>http://www.festivalmarrakech.info/en/personnalite/ahmed-fawzi-saleh/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2008, yabaye umuyobozi wungirije wa Rashid Masharawi. <ref>https://www.dohafilminstitute.com/financing/projects/grants/poisonous-roses</ref> Ku buyobozi bwa Masharawi mu 2010, Saleh yakoze ''filime ye ya mbere ngufi ya Living Skin'' yerekanwe bwa mbere muri 2011. Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yerekanwa mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime.

Hamwe nitsinzi yumukobwa mugufi, yahise akora poisonus rose muri 2018. Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku Isi mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya 47 Rotterdam mu gice cya Bright Future. <ref name="IFFR">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://iffr.com/en/persons/ahmed-fawzi-saleh "Ahmed Fawzi Saleh"]. IFFR<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">3 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> <ref name="egypttoday">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.egypttoday.com/Article/4/40881/World-premiere-of-Poisonous-Roses-to-take-place-at-IFFR "World premiere of 'Poisonous Roses'to take place at IFFR"]. Egypt Today<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">3 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> Iyi filime yaje guhitamo nkumunyamisiri winjira muri Filime nziza ya International Feature muri 92 Awards Awards, ariko ntiyatowe. <ref name="Egypt">https://www.tellerreport.com/life/2019-09-06---egypt-nominates-%22poisoned-rose%22-for-the-academy-award-.HJZ7iZtyLr.html</ref> <ref>https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/egypt-selects-poisonous-roses-international-film-at-oscars-2020-1237356</ref>

Yatanze kandi nk'umukorerabushake mu bikorwa byinshi by’imiryango iharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu mu Misiri. <ref name="IFFR">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://iffr.com/en/persons/ahmed-fawzi-saleh "Ahmed Fawzi Saleh"]. IFFR<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">3 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

